    "This looks like just the tool Bobby needs.",
    "But can they use it in their project?",
    "To answer this question, it is important to have a clear view of what the competencies present in the research team are, which tools and techniques the members of the team understand, and their motivation.",
    "Such an understanding of the team's skills, limitations and aspirations delineates the solution space available to the team and shows what routes are available for enlarging the solution space if needed.",
    "It also allows the team to make strategic decisions about what tools to adopt in the research project."
